name: Test Selected Code
description: Generate unit tests for selected code following project conventions
---
Generate unit tests for the selected code. Follow the project's existing testing conventions.

For Smart AI core code:
- Use Jest ^29 with TypeScript
- Place tests in an adjacent `.test.ts` file
- Use ESM imports (`import` not `require`)
- Use fixtures from `@core/test/fixtures.ts` if testing IDE/workspace operations
- Do NOT mock `@core/test/fixtures.ts` helpers beyond `jest.spyOn`

For other projects, match the existing test framework and style.

Aim for clarity and meaningful coverage. Include edge cases and error paths where relevant.
